    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Logs作为起点，中间层您想怎么命名？另外三个下游是Workbooks、Alerts，还有一个是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logs",
        "Workbooks",
        "Alerts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间层就叫LA吧，代表Log Analytics。三个下游是Workbooks做可视化、Alerts做告警，还有患者记录系统本身，全称HealthTech_PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LA",
        "Workbooks",
        "Alerts",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把结构搭出来：Logs指向LA，然后LA分出三条线到Workbooks、Alerts和HealthTech_PatientRecords。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logs",
        "LA",
        "Workbooks",
        "Alerts",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但HealthTech_PatientRecords这个名字在图上显示会太长，能不能简化一下视觉呈现，同时保留完整语义？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "可以用LA作为标签来承载这个全名，比如LA节点显示为HealthTech_PatientRecords，这样既简洁又能表达Logs到患者记录系统的直接关系。三个下游里Workbooks和Alerts保持独立节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LA",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Workbooks",
        "Alerts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这样结构清晰多了。LA既是Logs的汇聚点，又直接代表患者记录系统，同时向Workbooks和Alerts输出数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logs",
        "LA",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
